OpenSignal,is,an,application,that,allows,users,to,find,the,best,cell,phone,wi,fi,and,mobile,coverage,by,location,OpenSignal,provides,a,database,of,cell,phone,towers,cell,phone,signal,strength,readings,and,Wi,Fi,access,points,around,the,world,The,OpenSignal,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,and,data,of,OpenSignal,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,An,example,API,method,is,retrieving,coverage,information,by,location